caller_intent: Wakina wanted to make a payment for her mother's homeowner's insurance policy, but had previously missed the closing time and needed assistance with the payment process.
resolution_steps: Dana confirmed the payment intent and explained the new Friday closing time (3:30 PM).
They clarified the payment amount ($268.25) after initial confusion.
Wakina provided the Wells Fargo routing number (053000219) and account number (2380972477).
Dana processed the payment and offered to send a receipt via email.
Confirmed no additional payments were due for the policy.
knowledge_required: Handling account details and routing numbers
systems_referenced: Wells Fargo banking system (via routing number lookup)
summary: Wakina successfully made her mother's insurance payment after resolving confusion about the amount and providing banking details. Dana explained the new closing time and confirmed no additional payments were due. A receipt was sent for confirmation.
